<h2>Art Tracker Dashboard</h2>

<p>Use this tool to track where specific works of art are found. Click on the "Museums" button to see a list of museums in the database and the "Artwork" button to see a list of the artwork in the database. From those pages you are also able to add, edit, and delete museums or artwork as well as designate which museums are showing which works of art.</p>

<a href="/museum" class="btn btn-museum" role="button">Museums</a>
<a href="/artwork" class="btn btn-artwork" role="button">Artwork</a>

<h3>Add a museum:</h3>
<form action="/museums" method="post">
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="name">Enter the name of the museum:</label>
    <input id="name" name="name" class="form-control" type="text">
    <label for="location">Enter the location of the museum:</label>
    <input id="location" name="location" class="form-control" type="text">
  </div>
  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Add</button>
</form>
